## ğŸ†˜ Troubleshooting

**Having build issues?** See [BRAZIL_BUILD_INTEGRATION.md](BRAZIL_BUILD_INTEGRATION.md) for:
- Complete troubleshooting FAQ
- Common error solutions
- Debug commands
- Environment fixes

### Quick Fixes

**Build failing locally?**
```bash
# Fix virtual environment
rm -rf .venv
uv venv .venv
brazil-build
```

**PeruPython issues?**
```bash
# Check availability
which perupy-get-venv
# Should return: /path/to/PeruPython/bin/perupy-get-venv
```

